{"tid":304054,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好無安全感+ 過度敏感","createTime":"2017-06-30T15:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T17:15:23.000Z","uid":70483,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33baf6f37044f6b4514dd2fb814bc60ae634629b","tid":304054,"uid":70483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"我由細到大都係易呷醋、無安全感嘅人<br />\n每次男朋友有聚會、去旅行<br />\n俾我見到有親近嘅女仔就忍唔住要問佢係邊個等等<br />\n我都知咁樣好煩 <br />\n但真係控制唔到自己<br />\n佢已經好反感<br />\n我想同佢講，我係一個好無安全感ge人<br />\n不過都無用<br />\n有無人有相似經驗話我知點改<br />\n每一次都好辛苦"},{"pid":"a2c8d9d71ffe1d469c1b3621f55c2670aa33bad5","tid":304054,"uid":101367,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同ex一齊嗰陣都係咁 佢唔覆幾個鐘我已經可以諗好多野<br />\n<br />\n其實無計 反而睇佢願意做啲咩令你有多啲安全感 例如自己報行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd61724430fd3d2234489632366d34d891e40659","tid":304054,"uid":70483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同ex一齊嗰陣都係咁 佢唔覆幾個鐘我已經可以諗好多野<br />\n<br />\n其實無計 反而睇佢願意做啲咩令你有多啲安全感 例如自己報行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話:你再係咁都無人幫到你<br />\n我唔可以要求啲咩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f74b7458860f70542c543d8b590989a58ea9b0","tid":304054,"uid":120581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"0defd0eee125cdfd2d4ece407236fd6d52b1932c","tid":304054,"uid":36131,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同ex一齊嗰陣都係咁 佢唔覆幾個鐘我已經可以諗好多野<br />\n<br />\n其實無計 反而睇佢願意做啲咩令你有多啲安全感 例如自己報行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEx 話我安全感係要自己搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然自己都有責任去改善想法 唔好亂諗野<br />\n但我覺得對方自己有冇去建立誠信都係好重要<br />\n如果佢做嘅野本身就有考慮我嘅感受<br />\n咁就唔會話咩驚我唔開心先要講大話<br />\n明知我會唔開心<br />\n點解又要去做呢"},{"pid":"99306b27c4f2a94db0c4fd89c876cdcd8bb7c802","tid":304054,"uid":70483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同ex一齊嗰陣都係咁 佢唔覆幾個鐘我已經可以諗好多野<br />\n<br />\n其實無計 反而睇佢願意做啲咩令你有多啲安全感 例如自己報行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEx 話我安全感係要自己搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然自己都有責任去改善想法 唔好亂諗野<br />\n但我覺得對方自己有冇去建立誠信都係好重要<br />\n如果佢做嘅野本身就有考慮我嘅感受<br />\n咁就唔會話咩驚我唔開心先要講大話<br />\n明知我會唔開心<br />\n點解又要去做呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好睇人 <br />\n我有ex係真係秒秒鐘都知佢做緊咩<br />\n而家就無咁痴身嘅<br />\n但其實好專一係我唔放心"},{"pid":"4e4f8a8d95386058d1a96e92e87defc4bc814362","tid":304054,"uid":70483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:42:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"14923c0f9ffda77cd255c07072f63a2e5ad2029e","tid":304054,"uid":2990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但而家男朋友俾到好大安全感我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4cccbef3f86a5f1debd0322f30ff4b89957cb0","tid":304054,"uid":70483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但而家男朋友俾到好大安全感我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"b45c60bdab6b5b62d6b32a5dc12495e618350b75","tid":304054,"uid":20882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0