54f38068e254853b866361b8e1be00c5e18d","tid":304054,"uid":91729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:26:10.000Z","msg":"好容易亂諗野 <br />\n唔捨得但分左手 <br />\n唔想累人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9dd30d03ff94979ccd8e5f86cc58633bea6df1","tid":304054,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無安全感巴絲父母關係如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>自細離異</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n欠缺父愛母愛嘅關係更需要男女朋友嘅愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好好喎 不過細個父母忙冇人錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ee9fba8c6e1cf9bf143de82a429800c958e2a4","tid":304054,"uid":118645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無安全感巴絲父母關係如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>自細離異</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n欠缺父愛母愛嘅關係更需要男女朋友嘅愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好好喎 不過細個父母忙冇人錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1歲都冇老豆偷食...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3歲起就寄人籬下住姨媽啊婆個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係姨媽屋企比表哥比姨丈啲親戚摸過好耐細過乜都唔識過左十幾年到而家終於同返啊媽住都冇出過聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac76149587ea0ffe46f972b213db98bade775ab6","tid":304054,"uid":125846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"我啱啱分咗手..再上一次戴過帽 所以好冇安全感好敏感<br />\nEx其實俾咗好多安全感我 我知佢係專一<br />\n但自己都on9忍唔住成日問問問管住晒<br />\n結果佢最後都頂唔順 一分手就即刻識咗第二個<br />\n分手後我都有反省 其實好多問題都係好無意義<br />\n就算佢真係偷食 你問佢就會話俾你知咩？我以後都唔會再問呢啲問題<br />\n一樣父母係離咗婚 可能都關事"},{"pid":"595cc31cf255271a5ac11530a54341dc039095ca","tid":304054,"uid":70483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我啱啱分咗手..再上一次戴過帽 所以好冇安全感好敏感<br />\nEx其實俾咗好多安全感我 我知佢係專一<br />\n但自己都on9忍唔住成日問問問管住晒<br />\n結果佢最後都頂唔順 一分手就即刻識咗第二個<br />\n分手後我都有反省 其實好多問題都係好無意義<br />\n就算佢真係偷食 你問佢就會話俾你知咩？我以後都唔會再問呢啲問題<br />\n一樣父母係離咗婚 可能都關事</blockquote><br />\nSo true<br />\n就算佢真係偷食 你問佢就會話俾你知咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}